description: An assortment of dining experiences in one place
Traditional and specialty bagels and cream cheese spreads, Kosher Nova Lox and pizza bagels to hot and cold deli sandwiches, breakfast sandwiches and salads.
A fast-casual restaurant chain that serves Middle Eastern staples like falafel, hummus and pita.

Serving a full range of items from the classic 100% beef Big Mac and other specialty hamburgers to grilled and fried chicken sandwiches, fish sandwich, specialty salads, snacks and sides, fruits, yogurt parfaits and Happy Meals.
American Cuisine with a global spin. Organic & local whenever possible and specializing in gluten-free & vegan items.
Organically raised natural beef and buffalo burgers, all natural chicken and USDA prime steaks, sandwiches and salads.
An elegant wine country food menu includes locally-produced artisan cheeses, dry-cured meats as well as pasta and sandwiches.
